==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Scantily
<hw>Scant"i*ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a scanty
manner; not fully; not plentifully; sparingly; parsimoniously.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>His mind was very <qex>scantily</qex> stored with materials.</q>
<rj><qau>Macaulay.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><-- scantily clad, wearing almost no clothing. -->⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Scantiness</ent>⟦br⟧
